content:
{
    "inner": "I quickly glance at Max and then back at John. This doesn't sound like the kind of endorsement deal that is worth my time, but maybe there's more to his company than meets the eye. I take his hand and shake it firmly.", 
    "speak": "It's my pleasure, John.", 
    "action": "Shake John's hand firmly." 
}

{
    "inner": "I try to maintain a polite smile despite feeling a bit skeptical. Toasters aren't exactly the most glamorous products to endorse. But perhaps there's something unique about his company that could work in my favor. I watch as John demonstrates how the toaster works.", 
    "speak": "Interesting. How does your safety rating compare to other companies?", 
    "action": "Pick up the toaster for a closer look, examining the safety features while keeping a polite tone." 
}
